Description
-----------
The Wordcount client keeps track of the number of words in your Laxtex and Docx documents and periodically sends them off. The Wordcount server allows people to collaboratively monitor each others progress on writing assignments.

Instalation
------------
git clone https://github.com/circlingthesun/Wordcount.git
cd Wordcount

sudo apt-get install python-virtualenv python-pyside
virtualenv env --no-site-packages
source env/bin/activate
python setup.py develop
